name: presidential-debates-comments-clustering
description: At the point when we started this project, election week is coming up. There was so much excitement in the air on who is the next US president to be elected. There were thousands of articles on who's leading the polls. The US election has been trending on most, if not all, social media platforms. Being Data scientists, we wonder if it would be possible to leverage on these different data sources to understand various topics of discussion surrounding each candidate. Of which, we have decided to focus on Youtube comments as a starting point for this project.
